Good reaction

This is a female generic commoner to be placed in homes in the city core, in combination with either the generic male or the generic child.
Has the following selecteds:
initial, good
initial, average
initial, poor
secondary   -  only for players that have progressed to the point where they could ask her questions in the initial dialogues
pissed off    -  for everyone, once the player has threatened in the initial selection

Characters that use this dialogue will need to have separate tags, so that the local identifying them as having spoken to the player before will not cause hte player to be recognized by every instance of the character.

normal charisma

Set local on player identifying them as someone who spoke to this character before.
secondary, speaking to a player that has spoken to him before and progressed to the point where he would allow questions.

Set local on player identifying them as someone who spoke to this character before.
Chacks if the Beggar's Nest plot is done.
